{"tid":1908850,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"泰國將香港列入肺炎疫區 入境人士需隔離14日","createTime":"2020-03-03T14:31:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-03T18:01:55.000Z","uid":164771,"like":13,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"514aeac2dd175850f237aed07565e794c5f3c84e","tid":1908850,"uid":164771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T14:31:24.000Z","msg":"泰國副總理兼衛生部部長阿努廷今日宣布，泰國公共衛生部將指定香港等11個國家及地區為新型冠狀病毒肺炎（COVID-19）高風險地區。從11個國家及地區入境泰國的所有人士，都必須隔離 14天，沒有例外，不然將面臨處罰。<br />\n<br />\n泰國傳媒指，在泰國之外的地區中，將以下國家及地區定義為新型冠狀病毒高風險地區：日本、德國、韓國、中國（包括香港、澳門、台灣）、法國、新加坡、意大利、伊朗。公告內對於隔離場所和處罰事宜還未提及，具體隔離場所。該份公告在政府公報發布之日起第二日生效。"},{"pid":"f99e1f7e934ae832eba00f7ac818e48ff1f9ce39","tid":1908850,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T14:32:11.000Z","msg":"Why台灣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e61c99d3f003cd700a357e34f4fda649826bc44","tid":1908850,"uid":39092,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"f99e1f7e934ae832eba00f7ac818e48ff1f9ce39","tid":1908850,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T14:32:11.000Z","msg":"Why台灣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T14:32:48.000Z","msg":"奶共"},{"pid":"34f58e0130d6f8fbc1ca9a72d72656ee01f52608","tid":1908850,"uid":53466,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T14:33:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"647f3ce75bf208bd1a50dbb4b4c53da0903d6f0d","tid":1908850,"uid":164771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T14:45:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b36418b56f7a38f79099a724b80ea43d0aa8c576","tid":1908850,"uid":30396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T14:45:21.000Z","msg":"未Firm"},{"pid":"80a11d4e5528e507c3fc7c0c030fc92f89339aa6","tid":1908850,"uid":9055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T14:48:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />又唔copy埋下半<br />\n<br />\n不過香港旅議會總幹事陳張樂怡指，今日已向泰國當局求證，有限強制檢疫的限制僅屬泰國居民，港人出入境該國並無限制。<br />\n<br />\n而台灣傳媒引述台灣中央流行疫情指揮中心表示，據了解，泰方明天（4日）就會提出更新版本，一般來說，台灣人入境泰國並不需要強制隔離。"},{"pid":"2272dd61772904f62d4779c830cdbcaa49261522","tid":1908850,"uid":56532,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"80a11d4e5528e507c3fc7c0c030fc92f89339aa6","tid":1908850,"uid":9055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T14:48:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />又唔copy埋下半<br />\n<br />\n不過香港旅議會總幹事陳張樂怡指，今日已向泰國當局求證，有限強制檢疫的限制僅屬泰國居民，港人出入境該國並無限制。<br />\n<br />\n而台灣傳媒引述台灣中央流行疫情指揮中心表示，據了解，泰方明天（4日）就會提出更新版本，一般來說，台灣人入境泰國並不需要強制隔離。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T18:01:55.000Z","msg":"咁隔離黎把撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲on9過意大利"}]}